com.bosch.vn.capstone.jmeter

Class JmeterRemoteRunnable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bosch.vn.capstone.jmeter.JmeterRemoteRunnable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable, org.apache.jmeter.plugin.JMeterPlugin

    @Service
public class JmeterRemoteRunnable
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.jmeter.plugin.JMeterPlugin, java.lang.Runnable
    The Class JmeterRemoteRunnable use to run Jmeter Engine from Dashboard. It will call the Jmeter Api to run the Script, colect the data and save into db.
